{
  "id": "adv_card_ski_11_01",
  "title": "白石沙季",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "living-01-000-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "はい、はい……なるほど……\nぜひ引き受けさせて下さい",
      "startTime": 5.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "え？　千紗ですか？\n確かその日は……はい。私の方で確認してみますね",
      "startTime": 11.0317229703,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "また後ほどご連絡させていただきます\nはい……では、お疲れ様です",
      "startTime": 22.2333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4100.000000000002,
          "startTime": 26.3333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、お姉ちゃん帰ってたんだ。おかえりなさい\n今日はお姉ちゃんが、お夕飯の当番だっけ？",
      "startTime": 31,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "ええ。これから作るところよ\nそれより千紗。少し話があるんだけど、いいかしら",
      "startTime": 38.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "今、{user}さんから連絡があってね\n今度、星見市で開催される春祭りについてなんだけど",
      "startTime": 46.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "そこでやるミニライブに\n良ければ出てみないかってお話をいただいたの",
      "startTime": 53.4000015259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "わぁ……！　春祭りのライブにお姉ちゃんが出るの？\n昔、よく観に行ったよね。私、絶対に応援に行くね",
      "startTime": 61.7000015259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、私だけじゃないわよ。ちょうど予定も合うし\n千紗も一緒にどうかって話になっているの",
      "startTime": 72.3697997742,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "それって、また『白石SISTERS』でライブが\n出来るってことだよね……！？　うん、出たい！",
      "startTime": 79.4250881512,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ、{user}さんには\n私と千紗の二人で出るって伝えておくわね",
      "startTime": 85.6333368938,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう！　ミニライブ、楽しみだなぁ\nやっぱり、私達の持ち歌を歌うの？",
      "startTime": 93.3333368938,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん『つながる心Binary』は歌いたいわね\nでも、今回はそれだけじゃないわ",
      "startTime": 101.3666702271,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "ライブの持ち時間は、三曲分あるみたいでね\nサニピや月ストの曲を歌ってもいいんだけど……",
      "startTime": 108.8000035604,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01-ski011.m4a",
      "text": "この機会に、私と千紗、それぞれの『ソロ曲』を\n作ってみないかって提案してもらえたの",
      "startTime": 116.3666702271,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "私達のソロ曲を？　凄い……！　ファンの人達も喜んで\nくれそうだよ。それに、作ってみないかってことは……",
      "startTime": 125.2000035604,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01-ski012.m4a",
      "text": "私達でテーマを決めたり、歌詞を作ったり出来るわね\n私はぜひ挑戦してみたいんだけど、千紗はどうかしら？",
      "startTime": 136.0088203215,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "うん。うまく出来るか分からないけど、やってみたい\n気持ちを曲にして、みんなに届けるチャンスだもん",
      "startTime": 146.3666722616,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01-ski013.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、そうね。届けましょう\n私達の想いを、この曲を聴いてくれる皆に……！",
      "startTime": 154.1666722616,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01-ski014.m4a",
      "text": "私も千紗の曲が聴けるのを楽しみにしているわ\nもしリリースされたら、沢山買って千紗を布教しないと",
      "startTime": 162.7333389283,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "お、お姉ちゃん。気が早いよ～",
      "startTime": 167.1537103335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後の昼休み",
      "startTime": 172.0295545896,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 173.1228874048
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 173.1228874048
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 177.1666778565
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "いただきま～す。えへへ、今日のお弁当はお姉ちゃんが\n作ってくれたんだよね。わ、タコさんウインナーだ",
      "startTime": 179.3793223073,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 184.4962234816
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01-ski015.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、千紗の好きな卵焼きも入れてあるわよ\nそういえば、あれから曲作りの調子はどうかしら？",
      "startTime": 189.6666753134,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 194.0669365567
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "今のところは順調かな。テーマも決まったし\n決まるまでは、ちょっと時間かかっちゃったけど",
      "startTime": 198.6666631064,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "最初はゾンビだらけになった世界で\nみんなを応援するような曲っていうテーマにしてたの",
      "startTime": 205.1666631064,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 208.8592720352
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01-chs011.m4a",
      "text": "でも、それを{user}さんに伝えたら\n止められちゃって",
      "startTime": 211.5999964398,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 213.4659386161
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01-ski016.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうなのね。千紗らしいとは思うけど\n確かにちょっと、尖り過ぎかもしれないわね",
      "startTime": 218.5666631064,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 222.3833508654
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01-chs012.m4a",
      "text": "そうかなぁ？　みんなにも受け入れてもらえるように\n4怖ぐらいで抑えるつもりだったんだけど……",
      "startTime": 226.5666834515,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 230.2569788142
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01-ski017.m4a",
      "text": "尖ってるだけじゃなくて、怖い曲でもあるのね……\nでも、千紗らしい案だし、別の機会に使えるといいわね",
      "startTime": 234.9000167848,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 239.6699262146
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01-chs013.m4a",
      "text": "うん。{user}さんにもそう伝えてみる\nお姉ちゃんはどんなテーマにしたの？",
      "startTime": 243.3000167848,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 246.0056631252
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01-ski018.m4a",
      "text": "私は『アイドルとしての道のり』を、新曲のテーマに\nしたわ。これまでの軌跡と、そしてこれからの想いを",
      "startTime": 250.0666834515,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 256.1811732774
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_01-chs014.m4a",
